cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.CR 

The paper proposes a new method for improving performance in scene text detection using deep learning and ensemble learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also heavily relies on the predictive ability of deep neural networks, which suggests that it could also fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper proposes a new method for ensemble learning, which could also place it under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The application of the method is in scene text detection, which could also suggest categories such as cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
